Project on Ensembled Machine Learing Techniques¶

Deadline August 31, 2021

Selling personal loans¶

The given project1.xlsx file contains data on 5000 customers of a bank with demographic information such as age, income, etc., thier relationship with the bank like mortgage, securities account, etc., and the response to the last personal loan campaign. Among these 5000 customers, only 480 accepted the personal loan that was offered to them in the earlier campaign. The number of customers who are also borrowers is quite small, and the bank is interested in expanding this base rapidly to bring in more loan business and in the process, earn more through the interest on loans.

Natnael Alemu¶

Problem Framing¶

  • The classification goal is to predict the likelihood of a liability customer buying personal loans.

Data Description¶

  • the speadsheet has the following set of datas #### Nominal
  • ID : Customer ID, ZIP Code : Home Address ZIP code #### Ordinal
  • Family : Family size of the customer
  • Education : Education Level (1 - Undergrad, 2 - Graduate, 3 - Advanced/Professional) #### Binary
  • Securities Account : (1 - Yes, 0 - No)
  • CD Account : (1 - Y,0 - No)
  • Online : (1 - Yes, 0 - No)
  • CreditCard : (1 - Yes, 0 - No)
  • Personal Loan (Target Variable) : (1 - Yes, 0 - No) #### Numercal Data :- Interval or Ratio
  • Age : Experience : Income : CCAvg : Mortgage :

CONCLUSION¶

  • by using the below formulas we can compute the various validation parametrs Accuracy=(TP+TN)/(TP+TN+FP+FN) Misclassification_Rate=(FP+FN)/(TP+TN+FP+FN) Sensitivity=TP/(FN+TP) Specificity=TN/(TN+FP) Precision=TP/(FP+TP)
  • GNB Accuracy of logistic regression classifier on test set: 90.33% [[1253 89]

  • Misclassification Rate: It is often wrong: 9.67% [ 56 102]]

  • Sensitivity: When its actually yes how often it predicts yes: 64.56%

  • Specificity: When its actually no, how often does it predict no: 93.37%
  • Precision: When it predicts yes, how often is it correct: 53.40%
  • Logistic Accuracy of logistic regression classifier on test set: 92.93% [[1317 25]

  • Misclassification Rate:It is often wrong: 7.07% [ 81 77]]

  • Sensitivity: When its actually yes how often it predicts yes: 48.73%

  • Specificity: When its actually no, how often does it predict no: 98.14%

  • Precision: When it predicts yes, how often is it correct: 75.49%

  • KNN Accuracy of logistic regression classifier on test set: 94.80% [[1330 12]
